な巨大な積乱雲が立ちふさがる。\r\n\r\n脚本：山田靖智／絵コンテ：久藤瞬、中原れい、三宅和男／演出：三宅和男／キャラクター作画監督：しんぼたくろう／メカ作画監督：松田寛、山根理宏","status":"Air"},{"id":943028,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/943028","type":0,"sort":17,"name":"聖獣クアドルン","name_cn":"圣兽库亚多伦","duration":"","airdate":"2020-04-30","comment":15,"desc":"ようやく出会えた聖獣クアドルンは、ヒロト達ビルドダイバーズを拒絶する。しかし、ひるむことなくエルドラに対する想いを伝えたヒロト達に対し、クアドルンは重い口を開く。語り始めたその内容は、エルドラを襲った月の雷、そしてそれを放った元凶、アルスについてだった。\r\n\r\n脚本：イシノアツオ／絵コンテ：斎藤哲人、増田敏彦／演出：池野昭二／キャラクター作画監督：斎藤香、野崎真一／メカ作画監督：平岡雅樹","status":"Air"},{"id":943029,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/943029","type":0,"sort":18,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2020-05-07","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":943030,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/943030","type":0,"sort":19,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":943031,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/943031","type":0,"sort":20,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":943032,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/943032","type":0,"sort":21,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":943033,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/943033","type":0,"sort":22,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":943034,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/943034","type":0,"sort":23,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":943035,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/943035","type":0,"sort":24,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":943036,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/943036","type":0,"sort":25,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":943037,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/943037","type":0,"sort":26,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"}],"crt":[{"id":72144,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2b/cf/72144_crt_51jpS.jpg","name":"クガ・ヒロト","desc":"小林千晃"},{"i